HOWTO Install SGmisc from GitHub
--------------------------------

1.  Start an R session.
2.  Install package devtools, if not already installed:

    install.packages("devtools")

3.  Attach devtools:

    library(devtools)

4. Install SGmisc from GitHub::

    devtools::install_github("sgutreuter/SGmisc")

5.  Attach screenr and proceed:

    library(SGmisc)
